Output demo.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 900
Set Height 500
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20

Type "# claude-code-vitals — Know your limits before they know you."
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "pipx install claude-code-vitals"
Enter
Sleep 2s

Type "ccvitals --version"
Enter
Sleep 1s

Type "ccvitals status"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "ccvitals suggest"
Enter
Sleep 3s

Type "ccvitals -h"
Enter
Sleep 3s
